title: Good Directions 9613P Flying Duck Weathervane - Polished Copper
description: Gently gliding through the sky, this duck is looking for a place to migrate: preferably the rooftop of your house, barn, garage, or cupola. Our Good Directions' artisans use Old World techniques to handcraft this fully functional, standard-size weathervane that's unsurpassed in style, quality and durability. A great gift for wildlife  enthusiasts!
